                     <interp inst="t18240114-79-person777" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's wife, and keep a chandler's shop. I had served tobacco a quarter of an hour before. I found the tobacco a little distance from where the jar was found.</p>
